Class HeapdumpReader

java.lang.Object
com.ibm.dtfj.phd.parser.Base
com.ibm.dtfj.phd.parser.HeapdumpReader
public class HeapdumpReader extends Base
This class parses a PHD format heapdump file. To use it, first create the object (see HeapdumpReader(String)) passing the file name and then parse it (see parse(PortableHeapDumpListener)) passing it an object that obeys the PortableHeapDumpListener interface.
